text: Wouldnâ€™t usually post about a normal mom and pops coffee shop but was really surprised (positively to be clear) by the friendliness of the uncle and auntie. Made me feel right at home. Normal breakfast set is $3.10.

Their yuan yang($1.30) is smooth, medium thickness, less sweet and comes with coffee+tea aroma, a bits of mocha like smell. The stall owner is friendly and have many regulars patronized. Surrounding is airy and clean. Overall 8.5/10.
Nice coffee and friendly service! The auntie always makes my day better :)
